Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.30,0:00:16.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的风  格外的猛烈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.02,0:00:19.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洛伊德大人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.23,0:00:20.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.41,0:00:23.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱普希恩财团的贝尔格大人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.10,0:00:25.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.76,0:00:29.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将风之歌的力量给…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.20,0:00:32.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  经过这次的调整
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.26,0:00:36.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以放大海因兹大人歌声的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.64,0:00:42.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为我们的为了弄清楚普洛特文明系统的能力\N花费了过多时间的歉意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.57,0:00:45.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是  如果用了那个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:47.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给海因兹大人的身体带来的负担就更…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.11,0:00:49.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.69,0:00:56.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「西格尔均衡器」能力的开发已完成百分之45
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.41,0:00:58.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请您再忍耐一段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.44,0:01:00.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.02,0:01:03.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风一定会吹起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.37,0:02:41.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我两个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.63,0:02:43.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  来吃个痛快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.60,0:02:45.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.25,0:02:50.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裸喰娘特产海蜇馒头  一年一度的特价
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.52,0:02:51.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便宜地Fire
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.87,0:02:53.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,降价地Bomber
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.45,0:02:56.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种海蜇馒头可是很少见的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.17,0:03:31.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芙蕾雅酱好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.55,0:03:32.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要买海蜇馒头
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.03,0:03:34.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.45,0:03:37.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海蜇祭典啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.30,0:03:40.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是赞美拉格纳的海神大人的祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.20,0:03:42.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…那个我已经听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.64,0:03:45.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是任务
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.15,0:03:49.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,积极参加星球的仪式  和住民相处融洽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.80,0:03:52.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…这个我也听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.62,0:03:56.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情侣…是不是有点太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.60,0:04:01.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海蜇祭典是情侣们的节日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.81,0:04:08.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传说祭典的夜晚\N在海蜇星空下宣誓的情侣就可以永远在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:10.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海蜇星空下？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.04,0:04:12.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就等著看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.18,0:04:15.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28}　　　　　　　　　　　　　诱惑内衣\N{\fs45}今天晚上大家都穿决胜内裤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.71,0:04:18.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胜…胜…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.16,0:04:21.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾蕾  女孩子不可以说那种话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.48,0:04:24.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是个不守规矩的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.14,0:04:27.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恋人就可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.19,0:04:28.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永远的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.51,0:04:31.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿疾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.35,0:04:34.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小梅萨会来祭典吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.76,0:04:35.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.12,0:04:38.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  他明天就要走了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.55,0:04:41.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新的工作是在拉拉米斯星系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.89,0:04:44.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那附近好像没有狂暴者出没
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.77,0:04:45.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以放心了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.85,0:04:48.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉他又要各种不满意了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.38,0:04:49.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.52,0:04:56.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反应引擎的调整太随便了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.41,0:04:58.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Alpha小队的家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.59,0:05:00.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过会我去说说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.48,0:05:03.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己活着就好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.49,0:05:06.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在考虑那些事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.36,0:05:08.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.99,0:05:13.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉  还没有培养好Delta小队
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.05,0:05:15.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.47,0:05:17.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.62,0:05:21.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海蜇的孩子就算没有父母也能学会游泳的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.88,0:05:25.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅萨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.44,0:05:30.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  整理行李
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.43,0:05:33.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天大家会一起给你送行的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.80,0:05:37.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用费心了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.26,0:05:40.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈  死神混蛋对要小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.73,0:05:41.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢她？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.76,0:05:48.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他手镯里只有她一首歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.62,0:05:50.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为是救命恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.88,0:05:53.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能  那可是死神啊死神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.62,0:05:56.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  要小姐喜欢阿拉德
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.21,0:05:59.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能  鱿鱼干啊鱿鱼干
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.58,0:06:01.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三个人都好迟钝的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.90,0:06:04.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话就没法唱恋爱之歌了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.00,0:06:11.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢  阿拉德队长注意到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.52,0:06:13.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅萨中尉怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.46,0:06:15.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注意到了 还是没有呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.24,0:06:19.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真麻烦啊  喜欢直接说就是了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.86,0:06:26.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此  给阿疾分配重要的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.06,0:06:32.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到真的来了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.64,0:06:35.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你们已经不是我的部下了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.26,0:06:38.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.34,0:06:39.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,字面意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.16,0:06:43.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  最后了还这么讨人厌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.56,0:06:47.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有梅萨能继续吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.82,0:06:49.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做不了也得做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.12,0:06:51.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你很明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.31,0:06:54.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遗迹那边怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.64,0:06:58.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么特别的  只是个普通的石头罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.32,0:07:00.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过调查还在继续
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.07,0:07:03.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人的目标是遗迹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.30,0:07:06.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前的侦查方向肯定是那里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.65,0:07:09.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,袭击没有遗迹的星球应该是伪装
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.06,0:07:15.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,M女士通知了要加强拉格纳和沙哈的防御
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.56,0:07:19.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的有遗迹的星球应该就是这两个了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.74,0:07:25.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙哈  疾风和芙蕾雅之前都在那里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.73,0:07:29.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像和风之王国有缘分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.83,0:07:31.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疾风·因梅尔曼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.43,0:07:34.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.29,0:07:51.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是也真是有活力啊  拉格纳的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.23,0:07:54.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明不久之前才被敌人袭击了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.69,0:07:57.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会输给战争这种东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.62,0:07:58.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  女武神
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.94,0:08:00.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芙蕾雅也在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.22,0:08:02.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芙蕾雅最棒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.99,0:08:06.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢  谢谢大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.21,0:08:07.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.25,0:08:08.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好哒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.40,0:08:10.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芙蕾雅的支持者变多了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.78,0:08:13.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说你是间谍的人也少了好多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.90,0:08:15.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世态炎凉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.91,0:08:19.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  看样子是乘着风飞上天空了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.71,0:08:21.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.68,0:08:27.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边也是  进展顺利就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.64,0:08:31.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里是训练教官对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.81,0:08:36.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  也能带着自己的机体去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.64,0:08:39.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  应该不会再参加实战飞行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.34,0:08:43.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  为什么要我  邀请梅萨过去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.36,0:08:45.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是要撮合要小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.97,0:08:47.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.49,0:08:50.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过那样的话倒也挺有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.40,0:08:55.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想  如果能创造出美好回忆就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.81,0:08:59.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们都不知道  将来会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.74,0:09:06.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以要尽情享受当下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.83,0:09:07.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.30,0:09:12.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽情享受当下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.24,0:09:22.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.30,0:09:23.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.95,0:09:52.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒好棒  难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.24,0:09:56.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此  确实是海蜇星空下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.64,0:10:03.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每年的九月新月夜  海蜇一定会升上水面产卵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.64,0:10:07.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是所谓的生命的奥秘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.86,0:10:10.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个颜色是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.36,0:10:12.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绿色  黄色…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.30,0:10:15.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  是生命的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.20,0:10:32.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就算能长寿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.92,0:10:35.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不能尽情唱歌的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.05,0:10:37.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.47,0:10:39.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不能再尽情飞翔的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.75,0:10:42.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽情…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.77,0:10:47.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我也不是  只当个教官就能满足的男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.42,0:10:51.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮啊  梅萨君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.41,0:10:58.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.63,0:10:59.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.99,0:11:02.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AXIA
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.56,0:11:03.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这首歌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.65,0:11:07.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是拯救了我生命的歌曲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.34,0:11:08.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.60,0:11:11.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两年前  将我从失控边缘拉回的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.05,0:11:14.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你的歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.93,0:11:17.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为有你的歌声在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.40,0:11:20.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才能活下来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.89,0:11:22.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅萨君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.56,0:11:27.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的  非常感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.59,0:12:08.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洛伊德大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.76,0:12:16.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洛伊德大人  你要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.35,0:12:20.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海因兹大人需要休息
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.37,0:12:23.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.25,0:12:30.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久违了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.46,0:12:33.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有赢过我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.98,0:12:35.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是过去的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.74,0:12:42.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.94,0:12:44.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和白骑士大人不相上下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.25,0:12:59.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想违背陛下的旨意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.31,0:13:01.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  海因兹大人的生命…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.85,0:13:05.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,届时  就把我的命也献给崇高的风吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.25,0:13:08.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在赢了这场战争后
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:10.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的生命也…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.72,0:13:12.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收起你们的羽翼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.58,0:13:17.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,璐姆感受到了你们二人的风
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.06,0:13:24.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唱吧  我愿献生  基斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.45,0:13:41.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在沙哈出现狂暴症了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.39,0:13:42.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新配置的部队
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.05,0:13:45.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也瞬间被敌人控制了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.70,0:13:49.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心  那首歌正响着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.80,0:13:51.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.80,0:13:53.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比之前听得还清晰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.70,0:13:58.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普洛特文明的遗迹  正对敌人的歌产生反应
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.78,0:14:14.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死神  在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.85,0:14:16.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已开始和敌人交战
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.33,0:14:20.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行星里斯塔尼亚的遗迹也开始反应
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.45,0:14:21.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.74,0:14:23.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行星艾贝尔也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.18,0:14:25.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听到风之歌后  遗迹开始反应了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.96,0:14:27.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行星伊俄尼得斯也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.85,0:14:30.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  伊俄尼得斯应该没有遗迹的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.78,0:14:32.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  一听到歌声后…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.51,0:14:35.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行星图
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.75,0:14:41.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.81,0:15:00.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  这感觉是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.49,0:15:03.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然  遗迹会对我们的歌声产生反应
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.70,0:15:29.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁在…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.18,0:15:33.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这干扰是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.46,0:15:35.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.84,0:15:46.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.59,0:15:56.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洞…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.98,0:16:04.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美云
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.95,0:16:05.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小芙蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.92,0:16:08.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.68,0:16:10.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这阵风
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.73,0:16:19.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风互相掺杂了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.46,0:16:22.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人的歌声停了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.14,0:16:23.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一口气击溃他们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.43,0:16:24.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.16,0:16:26.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赌上  崇高的风
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.01,0:16:33.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被包围了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.85,0:16:36.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钳式攻击吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.66,0:16:38.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅萨不在的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.17,0:16:43.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.19,0:16:46.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小云  振作点  小云
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.30,0:16:48.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芙蕾雅  听得到吗  芙蕾雅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.69,0:16:51.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.68,0:16:54.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Delta 5
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.93,0:16:58.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白骑士大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.33,0:17:03.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙…白骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.42,0:17:14.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逮到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.00,0:17:20.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Delta  5
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.90,0:17:25.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  小喽啰放到后面再解决
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.05,0:17:28.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就趁现在要把女武神一网打尽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.56,0:17:29.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.41,0:17:30.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.17,0:17:35.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芙蕾雅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.22,0:17:40.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直没完没了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.86,0:17:44.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还以为能稍微乘上风呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.29,0:17:47.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.31,0:17:51.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.59,0:17:55.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.81,0:17:56.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.29,0:18:00.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Delta 2  迎战
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.64,0:18:03.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅萨？  你这是想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.65,0:18:06.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边的情况我已经听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.70,0:18:07.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然这样擅自行动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.75,0:18:11.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.25,0:18:13.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Delta小队的一员
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.57,0:18:15.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅萨君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.85,0:18:25.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.04,0:18:29.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.74,0:18:41.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要小姐你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.17,0:18:45.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.61,0:18:48.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为我唱歌吧  要小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.18,0:18:50.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅萨君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.69,0:18:51.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为我唱歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.15,0:18:54.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我完全「狂暴化」之前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.22,0:18:59.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.76,0:19:08.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了梅萨君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.81,0:19:12.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  要小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.99,0:19:50.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.95,0:19:52.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是异国人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.25,0:19:53.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白骑士？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.61,0:20:34.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙…就算变成了「狂暴者」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.39,0:20:36.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还能自如控制吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.29,0:20:38.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会如此凄美…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.30,0:20:43.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然和白骑士大人不相上下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.58,0:20:45.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是一阵不错的风
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.64,0:20:48.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能看得见风了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.29,0:20:57.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芙蕾雅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.24,0:21:01.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅萨…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.48,0:21:16.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得手了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.02,0:21:23.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死神  果然你也能乘上风吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.80,0:21:39.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.98,0:22:08.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅萨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.08,0:22:12.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅萨
